visual_name_counts = []
for place in visual_ad_freq_by_place.sort_values(0, ascending=False).head(20).index:
    visual_name_counts.append(df[df['place_of_publication']==place]['name'].unique().shape[0])
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
non_visual_name_counts = []
for place in visual_ad_freq_by_place.sort_values(0, ascending=False).tail(20).index:
    non_visual_name_counts.append(df[df['place_of_publication']==place]['name'].unique().shape[0])
